# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../developers.rst:179
msgid ""
"This should launch the OpenShot user interface. Any changes you have made to "
"the source code files (``*.py`` Python files, ``*.ui`` PyQt UI files, "
"etc...) will be included. This requires the ``libopenshot-audio`` and "
"``libopenshot`` libraries, and if anything went wrong with the steps above, "
"OpenShot will likely not launch."
